{"tid":1544179,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣開放東南亞免簽抗中國 韓國瑜：東南亞多來台賣淫","createTime":"2019-09-05T12:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T16:50:49.000Z","uid":144372,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1d79e4b1add267405ae1430ff6b4ed37d9294b61","tid":1544179,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/1676453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F1676453&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWG5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=39a2ffa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/1676453</a><br />\n<br />\n國民黨總統參選人韓國瑜昨日談及新南向政策，相關言論再度被質疑歧視新住民，引發熱議。來自越南的新住民藝人海倫清桃今（5）日於臉書上表示，韓國瑜的言論恐加深歧視，希望韓對此番言論道歉。<br />\n<br />\n針對日前一席「鳳凰都飛走了，進來一大堆雞」言論惹議，韓國瑜昨日又開直播解釋，稱是因為收到來自海關的陳情抱怨，有些來自東南亞班機的旅客，沒錢又不會說中英文，實在不知道來台的目的，「尤其最近查到很多來台賣淫、非法打工的，來台當『雞』賣淫。」<br />\n<br />\n對此，海倫清桃在臉書發文表示，現在陸客不來，很多做生意的老百姓，包括她自己在內，都很辛苦，大家也看到商店倒閉或收攤的很多，然而來自東南亞的旅客，可以說有部分刺激台灣的觀光和消費；但韓國瑜的這一段話，她認為，恐會造成對東南亞的朋友及在台灣的新住民誤會，甚至加重一般人對新住民在台灣生活的歧視。"},{"pid":"a5499690bde28f1b0ff193710612df6610acb718","tid":1544179,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:52:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1b6938fc5802d887cdbbab5cf8158bb28fde401","tid":1544179,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39993fd7b4f3d8eb393b8c0991c7fa642d013fc5","tid":1544179,"uid":266342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜，一個支那畜"},{"pid":"f0827e6e73939f6698dac99ea27d7c9f47c497ac","tid":1544179,"uid":56999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"一位西方記者問周總理：「請問總理先生，現在的中國有沒有妓女？」不少人納悶：怎麼提這種問題？大家都關注周總理怎樣回答。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周總理肯定地說：「有！」 全場譁然，議論紛紛。周總理看出了大家的疑惑，補充說了一句：「中國的妓女在台灣。」"},{"pid":"c414245ff407935161fd0f16784ce20ef7f83e27","tid":1544179,"uid":200070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:04:43.000Z","msg":"東南亞都來發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557e4fccadfc5da7da35d6f8c27a2bfa48f2f98b","tid":1544179,"uid":289179,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:05:55.000Z","msg":"到底佢要得罪幾多個國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1092b01b0f2b6de4e503247852ec078328dd6b09","tid":1544179,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:24:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cae5392bd0e1aeb6ce538e1859bad922254b3f7","tid":1544179,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:41:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"41fdc8890027f3df71eab8ce2a42a5b3c3d1036c","tid":1544179,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"沒人來怎發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0a6264bbcfcfd4d7d24230e7598da30557e454","tid":1544179,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:47:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"558dbb3449e8fb6c67dfdbdebd41ab14534f1e7e","tid":1544179,"uid":65984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:50:49.000Z","msg":"種族歧視, 仲要一次地圖炮全東南亞<br />\n<br />\n想選總統? 食屎啦你"}]}